-- China National Petroleum Still Supplying Extra Diesel for `Tight' Market
-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 2010-12-15T01:14:07Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-15/china-national-petroleum-still-supplying-extra-diesel-for-tight-market.html
China National Petroleum Corp. said
it is still seeking to boost diesel supplies as the domestic
market remains “tight” following a shortage of the fuel,
according to a statement on the company’s website.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Winnie Zhu in Shanghai at 
